[22/05/2019 13:54:39] <font color="#ffffff">en una ratonera.</font>
[22/05/2019 13:54:50] <font color="#ffffff">Pero yo no, me largo.</font>
[22/05/2019 13:55:16] <font color="#0000ff">Relincho.</font>
[22/05/2019 13:55:28] <font color="#0000ff">Disparo.</font>
