[22/05/2019 23:37:53] <font color="#ffffff">Coronel Stavros.</font>
[22/05/2019 23:37:57] <font color="#00ff00">Oh, no, no, señor.</font>
[22/05/2019 23:37:57] <font color="#00ff00">Me llamo Nontos Salonius.</font>
[22/05/2019 23:38:03] <font color="#00ff00">Ya se lo he dicho.</font>
[22/05/2019 23:38:03] <font color="#00ff00">Soy un pescador de Chipre.</font>
